{"tid":2222091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國至少32間大學現疫情，逾4000名學生宿舍隔離","createTime":"2020-09-29T00:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T01:19:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"923138d94bd39c1a7404f2b24c90ce21f3654e10","tid":2222091,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T00:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image2.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/hd/803963b0c3cffe54ffd25f750da2c9f1/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200928/_2020092813005432359.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F803963b0c3cffe54ffd25f750da2c9f1%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200928%2F_2020092813005432359.jpg&h=e4401440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肺炎疫情持續，目前至少已有32間英國大學在9月份新學期開學後出現了肺炎疫情，共有超過640名學生和教職工確診感染新冠病毒。<br />\n<br />\n據報，目前已有四間大學出現集體感染情況，其分別是曼徹斯特都市大學、利物浦大學、格拉斯哥大學和愛丁堡納皮爾大學。目前，全英範圍內大約有超過4000名學生處於在校自我隔離狀態。<br />\n<br />\n英國文化大臣杜永敦（Oliver Dowden）27日為政府要求學校安排學生返校開學進行辯護。他表示，重要的是，學生們不要因為疫情而放棄「生命中在校的一個學年」。<br />\n<br />\n杜永敦指出，「在這次危機中，年輕人付出了巨大的代價，我認為政府嘗試把他們重新帶回校園是公平的，因為政府有明確的指導方針可以讓學生們遵照執行。」<br />\n<br />\n而英國最大的反對黨工黨則呼籲，政府應慎重考慮在新冠肺炎疫情再次暴發後暫停學生返校學習，這意味著成千上萬的學生不得不在宿舍中隔離。<br />\n<br />\n英國大學工會表示，一直以來都在呼籲政府把網上教學作為當前疫情情況下的「默認選項」。政府要為學生們被迫在宿舍自我隔離的結果負責。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1884209/即時-國際-英國至少32間大學現疫情-逾4000名學生宿舍隔離\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1884209%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%9132%E9%96%93%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%8F%BE%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85-%E9%80%BE4000%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXLY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=172f1ee6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1884209%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%9132%E9%96%93%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%8F%BE%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85-%E9%80%BE4000%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2&h=92604202\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1884209/即時-國際-英國至少32間大學現疫情-逾4000名學生宿舍隔離</a>"},{"pid":"8c0182b327fb8d652c2b3a419b613af0a6191bba","tid":2222091,"uid":258921,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T01:11:30.000Z","msg":"讀名校嘅各位有難了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1921aefe33b3c249baa61bf271493a850c3dd0b7","tid":2222091,"uid":147467,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T01:12:40.000Z","msg":"中國可以抗疫就係因為無學生夠膽講咩students not criminals<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c51f8298d7db697dd43735474eb0da43d1f352","tid":2222091,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1921aefe33b3c249baa61bf271493a850c3dd0b7","tid":2222091,"uid":147467,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T01:12:40.000Z","msg":"中國可以抗疫就係因為無學生夠膽講咩students not criminals<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T01:19:51.000Z","msg":"中國堆大學唔俾學生離開校園，唔俾叫外賣，局學生食佢飯堂垃圾飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}